		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Unfortunately I'm deeply engaged in a project of my own right now... it's a tool I believe you'll all find useful though, once it's ready for a first public release. Getting there little by little... :)
<br />
<br />I had worldwide celebrities in mind, either living or dead. So in other words, if  you don't know them, they don't qualify. Former soviet dictators is a theme that always works, even if it's a tad cliche.
<br />
<br />Btw, Any reason why you feel the need to limit yourself to NROM for this project? CNROM or UNROM would certainly give you more freedom...
<br />
<br />"RUSSIAN ROULETTE: THE SOVIET MINDblowing GAME - FROM RUSSIA WITH GUN!"

		

