	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Still no graphics, but I've updated <a href="https://pineight.com/nes/#roulette" class="postlink">Russian Roulette</a> with more comments and compatibility with new versions of build tools.<br /><br />Changes in 0.02:<br /><ul><li>Updated for compatibility with cc65 2.14 series </li><li>pilbmp2nes updated for Python 2/3 compatibility </li><li>Factored out some PPU logic into subroutines </li><li>Switched to CRC16 randomizer </li><li>CHR ROM included with .incbin for fewer build steps </li><li>Removed some alignment padding </li><li>A few other micro-optimizations </li><li>More comments </li></ul>

		

